eiffel-tower-view-1.title: Eiffel Tower - View 1
eiffel-tower-view-1.description: Erected in 1889 as the entrance arch to the 1889 World's Fair, it has become both a global cultural icon of France and one of the most recognizable structures in the world. The tower is the tallest structure in Paris and the most-visited paid monument in the world.

parent.title: Eiffel Tower
parent.description: The Eiffel tower was built by Alexander Gustave Eiffel as the entrance arch to the 1889 World's Fair. Since then, almost 250 million have visited this iconic monument in Paris.
